OL,3,COfsted's single-word judgements should
OL,4,Cbe scrapped, says MPs
OL,6,FThe committee says that Department for
OL,7,FEducation and Ofsted should, as a
OL,8,Fpriority, develop an alternative to
OL,9,Fthe single-word assessments that
OL,10,Fbetter "captures the complex nature of
OL,11,Fa school's performance".
OL,13,FThe report also sets out other
OL,14,Frecommendations, including:
OL,16,FThe committee, made up a of group of
OL,17,Fcross-party MPs, began an inquiry in
OL,18,Fthe role of Ofsted in schools which
OL,19,Ffinished a few weeks after the
OL,20,Fconclusion of the inquest into the
OL,21,Fdeath of Ruth.
