OL,3,COfsted's single-word judgements should
OL,4,Cbe scrapped, says MPs
OL,6,FThe primary school headteacher took
OL,7,Fher own life after her school was
OL,8,Fdowngraded from "Outstanding" to
OL,9,F"Inadequate".
OL,11,FThe coroner ruled that the inspection
OL,12,Fcontributed to her decision to take
OL,13,Fher own life.
OL,15,FThe coroner issued a Prevention of
OL,16,FFuture Deaths report and said that
OL,17,FOfsted needed to make urgent changes
OL,18,Fin seven key areas to protect other
OL,19,Fheadteachers.
