OL,3,COfsted's single-word judgements should
OL,4,Cbe scrapped, says MPs
OL,6,F"We urge the new HMCI and government
OL,7,Fto consider a more nuanced system that
OL,8,Fcan provide value to both schools and
OL,9,Fparents, and as a first step we
OL,10,Fencourage the inspectorate, Department
OL,11,Fand schools to make more use of the
OL,12,Fmultiple judgements already included
OL,13,Fin reports."
OL,15,FThe committee has also requested that
OL,16,Fthe new Inspectorate of Schools, Sir
OL,17,FMartyn Oliver, update them every six
OL,18,Fmonths on the process of reforming
OL,19,FOfsted.
