OL,3,COfsted's single-word judgements should
OL,4,Cbe scrapped, says MPs
OL,6,FAn Ofsted spokesperson said: "We
OL,7,Fwelcome the Select Committee's report
OL,8,Fand its findings. We look forward to
OL,9,Fresponding in full to the
OL,10,Frecommendations.
OL,12,F"We have started making changes to the
OL,13,Fway we work, but we know more must be
OL,14,Fdone to address the pressures faced by
OL,15,Fschool leaders and staff.
OL,17,F"It is important that all changes we
OL,18,Fmake are done in the best interest of
OL,19,Fchildren and their parents and carers,
OL,20,Fthat is why we will launch a Big
OL,21,FListen in the coming weeks.
