OL,3,COfsted's single-word judgements should
OL,4,Cbe scrapped, says MPs
OL,6,FIt is the first time that criticism of
OL,7,FOfsted's single-word judgements has
OL,8,Fcome from an organisation outside of
OL,9,Fthe teaching profession and feels like
OL,10,Fa moment in the campaign for change.
OL,12,FThat campaign was started by the
OL,13,Ffamily of Ruth Perry. Her family set
OL,14,Fout to end the use of single-word
OL,15,Fjudgements after she took her own life
OL,16,Ffollowing an Ofsted inspection at her
OL,17,FSchool.
