OL,3,COfsted's single-word judgements should
OL,4,Cbe scrapped, says MPs
OL,6,FRuth told her friends and family how
OL,7,Fshe felt that "shame" and was worried
OL,8,Fthat house prices in the area around
OL,9,FCaversham Primary would fall because
OL,10,Fshe had "failed" to maintain her
OL,11,Fschool's rating.
OL,13,FOfsted has always argued that rating a
OL,14,Fschool as "outstanding", "good",
OL,15,F"requires improvement", or
OL,16,F"inadequate" is useful to parents.
OL,18,FThe Education Select Committee said it
OL,19,Fcouldn't find any significant evidence
OL,20,Fto support that theory and so it has
OL,21,Frecommended that they are scrapped.
