OL,4,Cbe scrapped, says MPs
OL,6,FInspections have now resumed and the
OL,7,Fnew Chief Inspector of Schools says he
OL,8,Fis going to carry out a listening
OL,9,Fexercise to better understand how he
OL,10,Fneeds to transform Ofsted and win back
OL,11,Fthe trust of the profession.
OL,13,FOfsted has already brought in some
OL,14,Fchanges since Ruth Perry's death, but
OL,15,Fit now appears that the pendulum has
OL,16,Fswung and single-word-judgements will
OL,17,Fgo - but when is anyone's guess.
